Overview

This project was developed as a Proof of Concept (POC) for Mangal Industries, a manufacturing leader in diversified industrial segments. The goal was to demonstrate the potential of data analytics and visualization in enhancing financial and operational decision-making.

The work included creating an interactive Financial Dashboard, mapping out a Process. All insights were generated using dummy/test data, ensuring that the business logic could be evaluated without breaching any confidentiality or compliance protocols.

Objectives

To simulate a financial performance dashboard based on manufacturing KPIs.

To present insights in a format suitable for stakeholders and leadership teams.

Key Deliverables

Power BI Financial Dashboard
Showcased key metrics such as Material Cost %, Gross Margin %, PBT %, Fixed & Variable Costs, and Sales Trends across quarters.

Process Flow Diagram
A high-level visual representation of operational steps involved in Mangal Industries’ business ecosystem.

Documentation explaining the scope, approach, and results of the POC.

Tools Used

- Superset BI for data modeling and dashboard creation
- Draw.io / Lucidchart for process mapping
- PowerPoint

